                            <comment id="19552" author="samokk" created="Tue, 12 Sep 2006 05:16:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I validated too early, I wanted to paste the following code :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;aop:config proxy-target-class=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;tx:annotation-driven transaction-manager=&quot;txManager&quot;  /&amp;gt;  &lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The result is that the class doesn&apos;t run in transactional mode, whereas it perfetly does if you remove the&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;aop:config /&amp;gt; line&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
